OL,3,C'I've got three children to feed':
OL,4,CMother struggles to make ends meet
OL,6,FPeople in are using food banks more
OL,7,Fregularly to cope with rising costs.
OL,9,FGuernsey Welfare Service has created a
OL,10,Fnew hub at the Bridge in St Peter Port
OL,11,Fto provide goods to those in need as
OL,12,Fthe number of times a household visits
OL,13,Fthem has risen by 30%.
OL,15,FLeonie Carre is a single mother with
OL,16,Fthree children and has been a regular
OL,17,Fuser of the foodbank for several years
OL,18,F- as a St Sampson resident, she is now
OL,19,Fable to go to one much closer to home.
