OL,3,C'I've got three children to feed':
OL,4,CMother struggles to make ends meet
OL,6,FLeonie's basic outgoings are
OL,7,Fincreasing, ranging from food to
OL,8,Felectricity, and she says it is a
OL,9,Frelief to know this extra help is here.
OL,11,FShe explains: "I've got three children
OL,12,Fto feed so as long as I've fed them, I
OL,13,Fdon't care. I will feed myself but as
OL,14,Flong as my kids have got food on the
OL,15,Ftable and food in the cupboards, then
OL,16,FI'm happy with that."
OL,18,FInflation in Guernsey, the rate at
OL,19,Fwhich prices are increasing, is 5.8% -
OL,20,Fmore than double that of the UK.
